% ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
%  The Kingdom of Axiomia — A Complex Logic Program
% ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

% ─── People ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Arthur is a person.
Guinevere is a person.
Lancelot is a person.
Morgana is a person.
Mordred is a person.
Galahad is a person.
Merlin is a person.
Percival is a person.
Gawain is a person.
Elaine is a person.

% ─── Gender ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Arthur is a male.
Lancelot is a male.
Mordred is a male.
Galahad is a male.
Merlin is a male.
Percival is a male.
Gawain is a male.
Guinevere is a female.
Morgana is a female.
Elaine is a female.

% ─── Family ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Arthur is a parent of Mordred.
Arthur is a parent of Gawain.
Morgana is a parent of Mordred.
Lancelot is a parent of Galahad.
Elaine is a parent of Galahad.
Arthur is a parent of Guinevere.

% ─── Ancestry rules ────────────────────────────────────────────
X is an ancestor of Y if X is a parent of Y.
X is an ancestor of Y if X is a parent of Z and Z is an ancestor of Y.
X is a descendant of Y if Y is an ancestor of X.

% ─── Sibling / family inference ─────────────────────────────────
X is a sibling of Y if Z is a parent of X and Z is a parent of Y and X is not same_as Y.

% self-identity is handled as a built-in by the engine

% ─── Titles and Ranks ──────────────────────────────────────────
Arthur has rank king.
Guinevere has rank queen.
Lancelot has rank knight.
Galahad has rank knight.
Percival has rank knight.
Gawain has rank knight.
Merlin has rank wizard.
Morgana has rank sorceress.
Mordred has rank prince.

% ─── The Round Table ───────────────────────────────────────────
Arthur is a member of round_table.
Lancelot is a member of round_table.
Galahad is a member of round_table.
Percival is a member of round_table.
Gawain is a member of round_table.

% ─── Loyalty and Allegiance ────────────────────────────────────
Lancelot has allegiance Arthur.
Galahad has allegiance Arthur.
Percival has allegiance Arthur.
Gawain has allegiance Arthur.
Merlin has allegiance Arthur.
Mordred has allegiance Morgana.
Morgana has allegiance Morgana.

% ─── Quests ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Galahad has quest grail.
Percival has quest grail.
Lancelot has quest rescue.
Gawain has quest green_knight.
Arthur has quest unity.

% ─── Skills ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Arthur has skill swordsmanship.
Arthur has skill leadership.
Lancelot has skill swordsmanship.
Lancelot has skill jousting.
Galahad has skill purity.
Galahad has skill swordsmanship.
Merlin has skill magic.
Merlin has skill prophecy.
Morgana has skill magic.
Morgana has skill enchantment.
Percival has skill faith.
Gawain has skill strength.

% ─── Betrayal and banishment ───────────────────────────────────
Mordred is a traitor.
Morgana is a traitor.
Lancelot is a traitor.

% ─── Complex rules ─────────────────────────────────────────────

% A knight of the realm: must be a knight, a round table member,
% loyal to Arthur, and NOT a traitor
X is a knight_of_realm if X has rank knight and X is a member of round_table and X has allegiance Arthur and X is not a traitor.

% A true hero: knight of the realm on a quest
X is a hero if X is a knight_of_realm and X has quest Q.

% A worthy grail seeker: must be a hero specifically seeking the grail,
% and must have purity or faith
X is a grail_seeker if X has quest grail and X is a knight_of_realm and X has skill purity.
X is a grail_seeker if X has quest grail and X is a knight_of_realm and X has skill faith.

% A magic user: anyone with magic skill
X is a magic_user if X has skill magic.

% A warrior: has swordsmanship and is not a magic user
X is a warrior if X has skill swordsmanship and X is not a magic_user.

% A rival: two people who share the same skill but have different allegiances
X is a rival of Y if X has skill S and Y has skill S and X has allegiance A and Y has allegiance B and A is not same_as B.

% Royal blood: descendant of the king
X has royal_blood yes if Arthur is an ancestor of X.
X has royal_blood yes if X is same_as Arthur.

% Rightful heir: has royal blood, is male, and is not a traitor
X is a rightful_heir if X has royal_blood yes and X is a male and X is not a traitor.

% Court member: either has a rank or is a member of the round table
X is a court_member if X has rank R.
X is a court_member if X is a member of round_table.

% Trusted advisor: court member, not a traitor, and either a wizard or has leadership
X is a trusted_advisor if X is a court_member and X is not a traitor and X has skill leadership.
X is a trusted_advisor if X is a court_member and X is not a traitor and X has rank wizard.

% Power couple: two people where one is male, one is female,
% both are court members, and they share an allegiance
X is a power_couple_with Y if X is a male and Y is a female and X is a court_member and Y is a court_member and X has allegiance A and Y has allegiance A.
